de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database

Class DbControlNodeInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbObject
      • de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.database.DbControlNodeInstance

  • public class DbControlNodeInstance
extends DbObject
    This class is the representation of a controlNode instance in the database. It provides the functionality to check for existing instances as well as creating new ones. Moreover it can retrieve all activities/gateways belonging to a specific fragment instance.
